column5: We have a small group heading there 1st week of June for a change of pace. Have fished the area lakes the last decade or so. Wabaskang, Cliff, Cedar and numerous back lakes. Anyone ever fished them, not much info to be found as far as we can tell? Thanks

Sorry, can't help, I hit on this post just because I don't remember even seeing a post on these two lakes. This could either be good or bad, depending on folks having poor luck on them, or such good luck that they want it to remain a secret! Ain't fishin' great? Bill
